Responsibility

Any use of SSB in:

operational decision-making

safety-critical environments

governance or compliance contexts

is undertaken entirely at the user’s own responsibility.

SSB provides structural admissibility discipline,
not authority, prediction, or guarantees.

SSB outputs are advisory and governance-oriented, not executable commands.


